page.title: 03My hobbies
page.content: My main hobby is football but I have to go out of the area to play for a team. I also swim and have to go out of the area to a recreation centre for this. At home I like computing and enjoy computer games and programming. I also watch T.V., my favourite programmes are Miami Vice, Hunter and T.J.Hooker. I also collect stamps from all over the world with my most expensive one costing fifteen pounds. I also practice bowling for cricket and play tennis against the wall. My favourite pop group is 'Tears for Fears'. I also enjoy badminton.
